description:
Learn SAP BW Modeling + Extraction + BEx Reporting by KIRAN KUMAR

A complete SAP BW comprehensive training for every one who wants to learn SAP BW from the scratch.

  1. Anyone can take this course with computer knowledge
  2. Learn SAP BW step by step from the scratch
  3. Step by step instructions with hands-on lab videos
  4. After completion of this course, you can work on SAP BW Projects
  5. Learn how to use Business Explorer (Bex tools) to create Reports using BW Data
  6. In-depth of BEx tutorials
  7. Learn SAP BW related ABAP programming
  8. Learn How to Extract Data from SAP R/3 Server/ ECC/ ERP
  9. Learn SAP BW LO-COCKPIT Extraction from the scratch
  10. Learn SAP BW CO-PA Extraction from the Scratch.

Finally, Do you have Zero knowledge in SAP BW and wants to Become Master in it. Then, this is right course for you in great plat form UDEMY.
title: SAP BW 7.4 ZERO TO HERO - MODELING
